{
  "text": "Assays for virus production and examination of the virus DNA. Culture supernatants and cell lysates of DI-transformed and tumour cells were examined for the release of EHV-1 virus particles by both plaque assay on L-M cells and by electron microscopy as described by [CITATION_1] . Infectious centre assays were performed to ascertain the percentage of virus-producing cells as described by Robinson et al. (1980 a) .",
